== 个人生活 ==
代斯勒有一个来自[[巴西|巴西]]的女友尤尼斯·多斯·桑托斯·桑塔纳（Eunice Dos Santos Santana）和一个名为拉斐尔（Raphael）的孩子<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.welt.de/lifestyle/article1139173/Dirndl-Revolte.html?nr=2&pbpnr=0 | publisher = welt.de | title = Dirndl-Revolte | accessdate = 2008-04-05 | language = de | archive-date = 2016-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818064454/http://www.welt.de/lifestyle/article1139173/Dirndl-Revolte.html?nr=2&pbpnr=0 }}</ref>，但仍然是末婚。在2007年，他开始写一本书。<ref>{{Cite news | title = "Dumm gelaufen, oder?" | url = http://www.tagesspiegel.de/zeitung/Sonntag-Sebastian-Deisler;art2566,2389712 | publisher = tagesspiegel.de | date = 2007-09-30 | accessdate = 2008-12-10 | language = de | archive-date = 2008-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081216023053/http://www.tagesspiegel.de/zeitung/Sonntag-Sebastian-Deisler;art2566,2389712 }}</ref>.

他的教育程度为[[应用科学大学|应用科学大学]]（德国教育的一种形式）水平，兴趣是[[篮球|篮球]]、[[食物|食物]]、[[音乐|音乐]]以及[[电影|电影]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.fcbayern.t-com.de/en/teams/profis/00377.php?fcb_sid= | title=Sebastian Deisler | accessdate=2008-04-05 | publisher=拜仁慕尼黑官方网站 | language=en | archive-date=2011-09-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110926232910/http://www.fcbayern.t-com.de/en/teams/profis/00377.php?fcb_sid= | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

